  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduo a Parole</title>

    <para>
      <application>Parole</application> is a DVD/CD/music player for
<application>Xfce</application> that uses
<application>GStreamer</application>.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

    <note>
      <para>
        Although this version of parole works with most files, it is unable to play
DVDs, reporting an error in the gstreamer backend.
      </para>
    </note>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informao do Pacote</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferncia (HTTP): <ulink url="&parole-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferncia (FTP): <ulink url="&parole-download-ftp;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Soma de verificao MD5: &parole-md5sum;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
