    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Dependncias de Parole</bridgehead>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Exigida</bridgehead>
    <para role="required">
      <xref linkend="gst10-plugins-base"/>, <xref linkend="gst10-plugins-good"/>
and <xref linkend="libxfce4ui"/>
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Recomendada</bridgehead>
    <para role="recommended">
      <xref linkend="libnotify"/> and <xref linkend="taglib"/>
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Opcionais</bridgehead>
    <para role="optional">
      <xref linkend="gtk-doc"/>
    </para>

    <para condition="html" role="usernotes">
      Observaes de Usurio(a): <ulink url="&blfs-wiki;/parole"/>
    </para>
  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalao de Parole</title>

    <para>
      Instale <application>Parole</application> executando os seguintes comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Esse pacote no vem com uma sute de teste.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>


